#Skill:  Swordplay [9580]
#
Usage:  USE @@@@

Time:   seven days

Use of @@@@ will cause the noble to spend time and effort practicing
swordplay, for use in personal combat.  Every seven-day use will
increase the noble's attack rating by one point.

Knowledge of Swordplay also allows the noble to train swordsmen,
knights, and elite guards, via the TRAIN order.
